sentences: Orhan Terzi (born 28 June 1964), better known by his stage name DJ Quicksilver, is a German-Turkish DJ and music producer.
His stage name derives from his days taking part in DJ contests, where a mercury column would gauge audience reaction.
Terzi was born on 28 June 1964 in Trabzon, Turkey.
His family moved to Hattingen, Germany in the late 1960s.
